properties.name: text
properties.value: Stopping to read any books you find is a good idea - they will contain important information about the world, or may even teach you new abilities. These first few books will explain the controls. Press 'W' to jump. Jumping while airbourne costs mana. Press 'Q' to close this book.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Ledge too high? Cast a teleport spell! Click and hold to charge the spell, and release to cast the spell. Remember, spell orbs are effected by gravity and you will teleport to the first place the orb touches.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Welcome to the training course. You will be guided through the abilities you have at your disposal to traverse the Monuments of the Old Gods. When you reach the end you will be granted full membership of the Guild of Explorers. Pull the lever to open the door and begin.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Multiple levers can effect the same platform in different ways. Some levers can also effect multiple platforms. Your path may be blocked until you activate the correct combination of levers.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Finding it hard to get a good aim for your teleport cast? Do not forget that you have the ability to control the spell orb while it is in the air. Just try moving as if you were the orb.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Bars or grating preventing you from continuing? If you aim carefully it is possible to manoeuvre the spell orb through the obstacle and teleport to the other side. Just be careful not to let the teleport activate before the spell orb has passed through.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Levers to open doors are not always directly next to the door they control. Sometimes you will have to explore other rooms to find the correct lever. We have not yet found a limit to have far away they can be, but often they are not too far off.

properties.name: text
properties.value: If the teleport spell collides with a wall but there is no room for you to teleport, the spell will not end. You can use this to your advantage to navigate through tight passage ways.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Another spell you should know is the bubble spell. Press 'E' to cycle through your available spells, and select the bubble spell and cast in the same manner as teleport. As the name suggests, bubble creates a large bubble that you can project away from you. The bubble is a physical object, and although it can stay afloat under it's own weight, it will slowly sink if you step on it. You should have enough time to use it as a temporary stepping stone.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Levers and switches can be found in some awkward places within the monuments. Our best engineers still have not been able to determine how the Old Gods were able to build mechanisms that, even all centuries later, barely need a flick of the wrist to activate.
